name: Garden Defender (BoneD4)
description:
This is for the Weekly Game Jam 233 with the theme "Gardening"

I thought I could finish it in a week, but it became really hectic between Christmas and New Year, and even got busier for school after that, which is why I'm submitting this 4 months late (yeah, really late). It's still better to see it through and finish it though!
